The Big Cheese is a one-touch-to-set,
enclosed mouse trap that protects
children and pets from accidental contact
with the trap. The semi-transparent

inspection whilst obscuring trapped
rodents from view. The trap is ideal for
use in home environments where
children and pets are at play, as well as in
kitchens and food prep areas. Use
multiple traps in severely affected areas.
Placing traps every 2-3 metres apart
will ensure the maximum catch.

Trapping Tips

Block entry holes, store foodstuffs securely

and practice good hygiene to avoid further

infestations.

Allow 48 hours for an initial catch.

If no catch, experiment as follows:

* Relocate traps to the area most affected.

* Try a supplemental bait such as peanut
butter or chocolate spread.
